# AI Face Detection Web App

A web application that detects human faces from uploaded images or webcam using AI.

## Tech Stack
- Laravel (Frontend & Backend)
- Python Flask (AI API)
- OpenCV (Face Detection)
- MySQL
- JavaScript

## Features
- Upload image for face detection
- Webcam capture and detect faces
- Display bounding boxes around detected faces
- Save detection history to database

## Architecture

Laravel Web App
↓
REST API
↓
Flask AI Service
↓
OpenCV Face Detection

## How to run

### 1 Run Laravel

php artisan serve

### 2 Run Flask AI

python app.py

### 3 Open browser

http://127.0.0.1:8000
